	* include/cpplib.h (BOL): Move macro to 1 << 12 since it is
	not used by C/C++'s unsigned char token flags.
	(DECIMAL_INT): New, using 1 << 6, so that it is visible as
	part of C/C++'s 8 bits of token flags.

