	(LINEMAPS_LAST_ORDINARY_MAP): Likewise.
	(LINEMAPS_LAST_ALLOCATED_ORDINARY_MAP): Likewise.
	(LINEMAPS_MACRO_MAPS): Strengthen return type from line_map * to
	line_map_macro *.
